  "title": "manager",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Oversee daily food & beverage operations to ensure smooth service</p></li><li><p>Manage staff scheduling, training, and performance</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with food safety, hygiene, and workplace regulations</p></li><li><p>Monitor inventory, ordering, and cost control</p></li><li><p>Handle customer feedback and resolve service issues</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with suppliers and vendors</p></li><li><p>Prepare sales, operational, and performance reports</p></li><li><p>Implement service standards and improve operational efficiency</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Bachelor’s degree or diploma in Hospitality Management, Business, or related field</p></li><li><p>Minimum <strong>2–5 years</strong> relevant experience in F&B operations or management</p></li><li><p>Strong leadership and people-management skills</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of food safety standards and local regulations</p></li><li><p>Good communication and customer-service skills</p></li><li><p>Ability to work flexible hours, including weekends and holidays</p></li><li><p>Proficient in MS Office and basic reporting tools</p></li></ul>",
